name: Bang-Bang Chicken and Shrimp
description: A spicy thai dish with flavors of curry, peanut, chile and coconut. Sauteed with vegetables and served over steamed white rice

name: Fettuccine Chicken Alfredo
description: This homemade alfredo sauce combines simple, fresh ingredients like butter, cream and parmesan cheese to make a rich topping to the fettuccine pasta. It is topped with tender sliced grilled chicken and then sprinkled with parsley

name: Baja Chicken Tacos
description: Soft corn tortillas filled with mildly spicy chicken, cheese, tomato, avacado, onion, chipotle, and cilantro. Served with rice and beans

name: Veggie Burrito Bowl
description: Cilantro lime, black beans, pickled red onions, toasted corn, queso fresco, shredded lettuce, pico de gallo, lime crema and sliced avacado, topped with portobello mushrooms brushed with lime-cilantro chimichurri

name: Spinach and Mushroom Flatbread Pizza
description: Spinach and Mushrooms with mozzarella, parmesan, garlic, herbs, and extra virgin olive oil

name: Parmesan-Herb Crusted Chicken
description: Sauteed chicken breasts coated with parmesan-garlic breadcrumbs and herbs. Served with roasted potatoes and broccoli

name: New York Strip
description: A juicy, tender, 16 oz New York Strip beautifully seasoned and drizzled with garlic butter. Served with a baked sweet potato and green beans

name: Fish Tacos
description: Soft corn tortillas filled with crispy beer battered fish, avacado, tomato, chipotle sauce, marinated onions and cilantro. Served with rice and beans

name: Italian Stuffed Shells
description: Shells filled with 4 Italian cheeses, spinach, in a five cheese sauce with a creamy bechamel drizzle

name: Spicy Cashew Chicken
description: A very spicy Mandarin-style dish with green onions and roasted cashews. Served over white rice

name: Fresh Grilled Salmon
description: Fresh Salmon grilled to perfection, seasoned with salt and pepper, splashed with a hint of lemon juice. Served with fire-roasted asparagus and wild rice

name: Thai Chicken Salad
description: Satay chicken strips, lettuce, carrots, rice noodles, cucumbers, bean sprouts, cilantro, peanuts and sesame seeds tossed with Thai vinaigrette

name: Sweet Potato Enchiladas
description: Warm corn tortillas filled with roasted sweet potatoes, poblano peppers, onion and melted cheese. Covered with marcona-red chile salsa, sour cream, and toasted pepitas. Served with black beans and cilantro rice

name: Chicken Picata
description: Sauteed chicken breast with lemon sauce, mushrooms and capers. Served with angel hair pasta

name: Grilled Steak Medallions
description: Grilled steak medallions served with fresh asparagus, shiitake mushrooms, sauteed cherry tomatoes, crusted croutons, mashed potatoes and madeira wine sauce
